This privacy policy applies to the Stations of the Cross app (hereby referred to as "Application")
for mobile devices that was created by Tom (hereby referred to as "Service Provider") as a Free service. This service is intended for use "AS IS".
This application does not collect or store personal data.
The Application does not gather precise information about the location of your mobile device.
If you installed this application from Google Play, then Google Play does collect some personal data. Please see the privacy policy for Google Play Services 
here: https://policies.google.com/privacy
